Quick Description
Easily connect your Frosting shop to Stripe to start accepting payments.

Numbered Detail List:
<dl>
<dt>1</dt>
<dd>Hover over the ***User*** icon on the top menu bar.  Click on ***Shop Manager*** </dd></dl>

![Shop Manager Top Bar](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Menu+%3E+Click+Shop+Manager.png)

<dt>2</dt>
<dd>From the Shop Manager, click on ***Settings***.</dd></dl>

![Hover Settings](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Hover+Settings.png)

<dl><dt>3</dt>
<dd>Click on **Payment**.</dd></dl>

![Click on Payment](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Hover+Settings%3EPayment.png)

<dl><dt>4</dt>
<dd>Click on the ***Connect with Stripe*** button.</dd></dl>

![Click Connect with Stripe](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Payment+Connect+with+Stripe.png)

<dt>5</dt>
<dd>You will be taken to Stripe to create or to log in to an existing account.</dd>
### Create an account  
<dd>Once you have filled out all of the details, click ‘Authorize access to this Account’ and you will be connected to Frosting and will be able to accept payments!</dd>

![Stripe Authorize access to this account](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Payment+Connect+with+Stripe+-+Authorize+Account.png)

### Log in to an existing account  

<dd>If you already have an account you can click on ***Sign in***</dd>

![Stripe Login](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Payment+Connect+with+Stripe+-+Sign+Into+Stripe+Account.png)

<dt>6</dt>
<dd>Click on ***Payment***.</dd>

![Click on Payment](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Hover+Settings%3EPayment.png)

<dt>7</dt>
<dd>Click on ***Payment***.</dd>

![Click on Payment](https://frosting-public-helpdocsfiles.s3.amazonaws.com/Help+Scout+Screenshots/Hover+Settings%3EPayment.png)



